text: Abramovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Semyonovskoye Rural Settlement of Verkhnekhavsky District, Voronezh Oblast, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == References == Category:Rural localities in Verkhnekhavsky District
title: Abramovka, Verkhnekhavsky District, Voronezh Oblast
